%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5e28c2e20bb6c4240a55d8edffb777ec, type: 3}
  m_Name: ChimeFinalNeutral
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NewDialogueData
  npcName: Echo
  dialogueLines:
  - LineID: Start
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Echo!
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: II
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: II
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Chime?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: III
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: III
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Are you okay?! You were corrupted, I had to fight this awful version of
      you.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: IV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: IV
    Speaker: Echo
    text: I...couldn't control myself. Everything came back to me. This pendant,
      you gave it to me. It's the reason I'm here, right?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: V
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: V
    Speaker: Chime
    text: ...It's one of the reasons, yes. I'm so sorry, Echo. I didn't want you
      to find out this way.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: VI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VI
    Speaker: Echo
    text: You didn't want me to find out that we were best friends and that I'd lost
      you? I don't understand.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: VII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VII
    Speaker: Chime
    text: It's not that simple, Echo. I called to you from the other side, here in
      the Astral Plane, through the pendant I gave you all those years ago.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: VIII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VIII
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Basically, you pulled me in here with the goal of helping you, but a side
      effect of the means you used was giving me amnesia?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: IX
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: IX
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Yes. I wanted to find the right time to tell you everything, but by the
      time the rumbling started and you had touched the tree...everything just moved
      so fast.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: X
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: X
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Why me? Someone else could have helped you more, don't you think?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XI
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Why you? Echo...nobody else meant as much to me as you did, as you do.
      I gave you the pendant, remember? All the time we spent together?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XII
    Speaker: Echo
    text: ...
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XIII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XIII
    Speaker: Echo
    text: I just can't understand why you'd go out of your way to do all this. Why
      couldn't I have just stayed back?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XIV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XIV
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Oh, Echo...you still haven't learnt the lesson. You still don't know how
      much you meant to me, how much good you gave to the world.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XV
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Maybe...when you close your eyes...you'll figure it out...in the next...
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 1
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
